title: Hawai'i Volume 1
description: 15 Hawaiian island style acoustic tracks for your happy and soft moments
longDescription:
Preview the collection:

  • Hawaii Vol.1 su YouTube


Hawaii - Volume 1 features 15 Hawaiian island style themes suitable for your tropical 

worlds. The arrangements include premium tenor ukulele, steel guitar, marimba, 

guitars and many types of percussions. 

Every music theme comes with multiple loops and shorter edits for further usage.


  • Hawaiian Flower: Full length (01:38), 3 Edits, 5 Loops, Intro & Outro 
  • Hawaiian Fun Time: Full length (02:10), 3 Edits, 8 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Hawaiian Lava: Full length (02:05), 4 Edits, 6 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Hawaiian Love Story: Full length (01:43), 2 Edits, 7 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Hawaiian Luau: Full length (01:31), 2 Edits, 8 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Hawaiian Sunrise: Full length (02:05), 2 Edits, 5 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Hawaiian Ukulele Bubbles: Full length (01:41), 2 Edits, 5 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Hawaiian Ukulele Summer: Full length (01:39), 4 Edits, 9 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Hawaiian Ukulele Turtles: Full length (01:33), 2 Edits, 5 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Kalakaua Avenue: Full length (00:35), 1 Edits, 3 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Kaneohe Moon: Full length (02:51), 3 Edits, 7 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Picnic With My Ukulele: Full length (02:18), 4 Edits, 7 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Strumming My Ukulele In Waikiki: Full length (02:49), 2 Edits, 12 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Summer In Honolulu: Full length (02:15), 2 Edits, 8 Loops, Intro & Outro
  • Suppa Flash Ukulele: Full length (02:00), 2 Edits, 7 Loops, Intro & Outro


Take a look: Total Game Music Collection - 500 High Quality music themes ideal for any game!

Maybe you might be interested at Acoustic Vol.2


This pack is produced by Luca Tomassini a composer with more than 20 years of expertise in music production with multiple TV, feature films and multimedia placements.
